name: Student LIST Report
query:
select
    sl.name as "Name",sl.school as "School", sl.school_name as "School Name", sl.academic_year as "Academic Year", sl.program as "Program", sl.section_name as "Section Name", sr.student_name as "Student name",sr.roll_number as "Roll Number", sr.conatct_number as "Conatct Number", sr.email as "Email"
from
    `tabStudents List`sl,
    `tabStudent records`sr
    
where
sr.parent = sl.name
